creator: CheckedOK
descriptionHtml:
Safeguard Weekly by Hoistech is a turnkey asset management package designed specifically for our clients to manage the weekly inspection and record-keeping requirements of their lifting and height safety assets.

Safeguard Weekly by Hoistech is designed for use on mobile devices by asset owners as well as providing access to reports and data through a web portal.
descriptionShort: Safeguard Weekly by Hoistech is a turn key asset management package
